CLARIFICATION ON SIMULATION OUTPUT:
The Software is a decision-support and learning tool designed to expose governance-
resilience gaps under pressure. It is NOT a prediction engine, intelligence system, 
or authoritative model of real-world space governance. Simulation outputs are based on 
programmed scenario logic and game theory, not machine learning, real data, or 
classified intelligence. Users should treat Polaris as a pedagogical aid and 
governmental stress-testing tool, not as a substitute for expert policy analysis, 
real intelligence, or multilateral negotiation.

